ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v281.group

Class DER_O44_DONOR

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v281.group.DER_O44_DONOR
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class DER_O44_DONOR
extends AbstractGroup

    Represents a DER_O44_DONOR group structure (a Group object). A Group is an ordered collection of message segments that can repeat together or be optionally in/excluded together. This Group contains the following elements:

    • 1: PID (Patient Identification)
    • 2: PD1 (Patient Additional Demographic) optional
    • 3: OBX (Observation/Result) optional repeating
    • 4: NTE (Notes and Comments) optional repeating
    • 5: AL1 (Patient Allergy Information) optional repeating
    • 6: ARV (Access Restriction) optional repeating
    • 7: DER_O44_DONOR_REGISTRATION (a Group object) optional
    See Also:
